`x.AdvertisementPositionFKNavigation`.`PageUrl`, `x.AdvertisementPositionFKNavigation`.`Status`, `x.AdvertisementPositionFKNavigation`.`Title`, `x.AdvertisementPositionFKNavigation`.`Width`
FROM `AdvertisementContents` AS `x`
LEFT JOIN `WebMasters` AS `x.WebMasterCensorFKNavigation` ON `x`.`CensorFK` = `x.WebMasterCensorFKNavigation`.`KeyId`
LEFT JOIN `User` AS `x.WebMasterCensorFKNavigation.UserBy` ON `x.WebMasterCensorFKNavigation`.`UserFK` = `x.WebMasterCensorFKNavigation.UserBy`.`Id`
INNER JOIN `Advertisers` AS `x.AdvertiserFKNavigation` ON `x`.`AdvertiserFK` = `x.AdvertiserFKNavigation`.`KeyId`
INNER JOIN `AdvertisementPositions` AS `x.AdvertisementPositionFKNavigation` ON `x`.`AdvertisementPositionFK` = `x.AdvertisementPositionFKNavigation`.`KeyId`
WHERE `x`.`AdvertiserFK` = @__advertiserId_0
ORDER BY `x`.`KeyId`
LIMIT @__p_2 OFFSET @__p_1" (0723d8ff)
